  allLines:
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "See, I really don\u2019t think I\u2019d do a good job since I only
      did it for a short time as an amateur and frankly... I was a pretty shit DJ.
      Buuut I can prepare a setlist for you, if you\u2019d like. I used to work at
      a radio station so I\u2019m pretty well-versed in researching music for specific
      groups of people.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: -6843144879011698485, guid: 1af55f43fff034e4297b2207808da62a, type: 3}
    sentence: "Oh radio? You\u2019re into the old tech, I see. It\u2019s cool that
      you know your shit though sooo I guess I can trust you with my next epic party
      playlist."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 7956698841550424776, guid: 2dfa7703027856e42aa0ad06571044c3, type: 3}
    sentence: "Sounds good! Also, you don\u2019t really have to pay me for making
      a playlist. I wouldn\u2019t wanna feel like I\u2019m scamming you or anything"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: -6843144879011698485, guid: 1af55f43fff034e4297b2207808da62a, type: 3}
    sentence: "Scamming me? Baby no party gets a DJ this hot for free, I don\u2019t
      mind paying for your ride, your accomodation or your breakfast. (muttered)
      although technically you\u2019re still not a DJ..."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 7956698841550424776, guid: 2dfa7703027856e42aa0ad06571044c3, type: 3}
    sentence: Oh.. haha, if you insist then we can get breakfast the morning after.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Awww that\u2019s cute, well done newbie. Although don\u2019t tell
      them they can\u2019t exchange personal information just yet, I don\u2019t wanna
      ruin the moment."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 3
    characterName: Chaperon
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "They can\u2019t? Why?"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Just imagine you were on a date with some guy... or girl. Whatever
      you\u2019re into. And then that person suddenly started to say weird **** like
      (man voice)..."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "\u201CHey girl you look like you\u2019d look real good in a maid costume,
      yeah let me take you back to mine.\u201D"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 3
    characterName: Chaperon
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Ohhkay...
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Ne-Nevermind the example, just saying that there are some creeps even
      we can\u2019t catch with our scans. We don\u2019t want to risk anyone\u2019s
      safety before they\u2019re sure they want to continue seeing each other after
      the second date."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Then, we can risk their safety?
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "HAHAHAHAAHAHAHA YOU\u2019RE A FUNNY ONE SO FU-"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
